  const safeUsers = users.map(({ id, name }) => ({ id, name }));
  res.json(safeUsers);
});
```

### 6. No CORS Configuration (OWASP A05: Security Misconfiguration)

There is no CORS policy. By default Express doesn't add CORS headers (so browsers will block cross-origin requests), but this should be **explicitly configured** rather than left implicit.

**Recommendation:**

```js
